open, a simple door opener
executable location: '/bin/open.sh'  alias:'open'
open is part of the 'open' app

syntax: 'open doorname duration'
duration is optional, use 0 for toggle

door names can be searched with 'dhcp lookup'
any registered name can be called, if there
is the program "door" on the other side then 
they will see if the current user is allowed
to open that door attached, and then open it.

very simple, very robust.
duration is in seconds, use 0 to toggle it on/off